  "prompt": "Any suggested cellphone units to make me active on messanger all the time using only my data?",
  "response": "To stay active on Messenger using only your mobile data, you'll want a smartphone that has a good balance of battery life, performance, and data efficiency. Here are some suggestions for cellphones that excel in these areas, across various price ranges:\n\n### Budget Options\n1. **Moto G Power (2023)**\n   - Excellent battery life (up to 3 days)\n   - A solid performance with a decent processor\n   - Affordable price point\n\n2. **Samsung Galaxy A32**\n   - Good battery life and display\n   - Reliable performance for social media apps\n   - Affordable and offers good value\n\n### Mid-Range Options\n3. **Google Pixel 6a**\n   - Great camera and software optimization\n   - Clean Android experience, which can help with data usage efficiency\n   - Good battery life and software support\n\n4. **Samsung Galaxy A53**\n   - Solid performance and good battery life\n   - 5G capable (if you have access to 5G data)\n   - Good display for media consumption\n\n### Premium Options\n5. **Apple iPhone 14**\n   - Excellent performance and battery management\n   - Built-in optimization for data usage with iOS\n   - Long-term software support\n\n6. **Samsung Galaxy S23**\n   - Top-notch performance and camera\n   - Improved battery life compared to previous models\n   - 5G support for faster data speeds\n\n### Tips for Data Efficiency:\n- **Set Background Data Usage**: Allow Messenger to use data in the background so you can receive messages in real-time.\n- **Use Data Saver Mode**: Many smartphones have a data saver mode, which can help you manage your data usage better.\n- **Limit App Usage**: Instead of leaving multiple apps open, close those not in use to conserve battery and data.\n\nUltimately, the best choice will depend on your budget and specific feature preferences. If staying active on Messenger is your main goal, focus on devices that offer excellent battery performance and solid internet connectivity.",
